  "designRationale": {
    "layoutDecisions": "The layout employs a vertical list to maximize screen real estate on mobile, aligning with user constraints.  Items are spaced 24px apart for visual breathing room and improved tap targets. Top and bottom padding ensures content doesn't feel cramped against the edges.",
    "userFlowReasoning": "The user flow is straightforward: the settings are presented in a clear, logical order, facilitating quick access and modification.  Primary actions are prominently displayed while secondary actions are easily accessible. A confirmation dialog is included for irreversible actions like account deletion to prevent accidental actions.",
    "componentChoices": "The App Bar provides a clear header with app title.  List items are used for individual settings, offering clear labels and space for potential indicators. The Bottom Navigation Bar provides standard navigation options, ensuring easy access to other parts of the app. Buttons are used for primary actions.",
    "visualHierarchy": "Visual hierarchy is established through spacing, typography, and color.  Headers and primary actions are given higher prominence through typography size and primary color use. Secondary elements utilize secondary color and smaller typography size. This ensures clarity in navigation and actions."
  },
